---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="GolfTV | Digital Advertising for Golf Course Clubhouses | SDN"
  description="SDN installs digital advertising screens in golf course clubhouses, sells the ad space, and shares revenue with your course. You pay nothing."
  canonicalPath="/golftv/"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Your clubhouse visitors are worth more than you think</h1>
    <p>SDN installs digital advertising screens in golf course clubhouses, sells the ad space, and shares the revenue with your course. You pay nothing.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="lead">Golf course clubhouses are one of the most under-monetized advertising environments in Canada.</p>
      <p>Your members and guests spend 30-60 minutes in the clubhouse before and after their rounds — eating, drinking, socializing, waiting for tee times, and browsing the pro shop.</p>
      <p>They're affluent, they're relaxed, and they're exactly the audience that premium brands want to reach. SDN helps you capture that value without any cost or effort from your team.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why golf courses are premium advertising venues</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Golf course visitors represent one of the most desirable consumer demographics in Canadian advertising:</p>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Affluence</h3>
          <p>The average Canadian golfer has a household income significantly above the national median. Members of private clubs skew even higher. This is an audience that makes premium purchasing decisions — vehicles, financial services, travel, luxury goods, real estate, and home improvement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Dwell time</h3>
          <p>A round of golf takes 4+ hours, but the advertising opportunity is in the clubhouse. Members and guests spend 30-60 minutes pre-round (checking in, warming up, having coffee) and 30-60 minutes post-round (dining, socializing, using the bar). That's substantial time in front of our screens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Receptivity</h3>
          <p>Golfers are in a relaxed, positive environment. Research consistently shows that consumers are more receptive to advertising messages when they're in a good mood and a comfortable setting. A golf clubhouse is exactly that.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Repeat visitation</h3>
          <p>Regular members play 40-80+ rounds per year. Even casual visitors return multiple times per season. Advertisers get repeated exposure to the same high-value audience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="install-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What SDN installs in your clubhouse</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">We install 1-3 screens per golf course, positioned where your members and guests spend time:</p>
      <div class="install-grid">
        <div class="install-card">
          <h3>Main clubhouse lounge / bar area</h3>
          <p>Where members gather before and after rounds</p>
        </div>
        <div class="install-card">
          <h3>Pro shop</h3>
          <p>Where golfers browse equipment and check in</p>
        </div>
        <div class="install-card">
          <h3>Restaurant / dining area</h3>
          <p>Where visitors sit for meals and drinks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="install-card">
          <h3>Hallway / entrance</h3>
          <p>High-traffic corridors</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="install-note">Screens are 65"–86" commercial-grade 4K displays — the same professional hardware we install in our arena network. They're appropriate for the premium environment of a golf clubhouse.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What runs on the screens</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Content is tailored for the golf environment:</p>
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Advertising (~50% of screen time)</h3>
          <p>Premium brand campaigns and local business ads relevant to your membership demographic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Weather</h3>
          <p>Current conditions and multi-day forecasts (golfers check weather constantly)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Sports scores</h3>
          <p>PGA Tour leaderboards, NHL/MLB/NFL scores</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Course information</h3>
          <p>Tee time availability, event schedules, tournament results</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Clubhouse promotions</h3>
          <p>Your pro shop specials, dining features, membership offers</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="content-note">The content keeps the screens relevant and useful, which keeps eyes on them — and makes the advertising more effective.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="revenue-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Revenue for your course</h2>
      <div class="revenue-grid">
        <div class="revenue-card">
          <h3>How it works</h3>
          <p>SDN sells advertising inventory on your clubhouse screens to a mix of national brands and local businesses. You receive a guaranteed monthly revenue-share per agreement — deposited to your account every month for the duration of our partnership.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="revenue-card">
          <h3>Who advertises at golf courses?</h3>
          <p>The premium demographics of golf course visitors attract advertisers from categories like:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Automotive — luxury and premium vehicle brands, dealerships</li>
            <li>Financial services — wealth management, private banking, insurance</li>
            <li>Travel — resort destinations, airlines, cruise lines</li>
            <li>Real estate — luxury home developers, realtors</li>
            <li>Healthcare — private clinics, dental, vision care</li>
            <li>Home improvement — premium renovation, landscaping, smart home</li>
            <li>Food and beverage — restaurants, wine, spirits</li>
            <li>Local services — businesses near your course that serve your membership</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="factors-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Revenue factors</h2>
      <div class="factors-grid">
        <div class="factor-item">
          <strong>Membership size and guest volume</strong>
          <span>More visitors = more impressions = more ad revenue</span>
        </div>
        <div class="factor-item">
          <strong>Market</strong>
          <span>Courses in major metro areas attract more advertising demand</span>
        </div>
        <div class="factor-item">
          <strong>Course profile</strong>
          <span>Private clubs command premium rates due to audience demographics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="factor-item">
          <strong>Number of screens</strong>
          <span>More screens capture more of the clubhouse traffic</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="clublink-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our golf course partnership: ClubLink</h2>
      <p>SDN operates screens in 26 ClubLink golf courses across Ontario — the largest private golf course network in Canada. This partnership demonstrates how golf course digital advertising works at scale:</p>
      <ul class="clublink-list">
        <li>Screens installed in every clubhouse at no cost to ClubLink</li>
        <li>National brand campaigns run alongside local business advertising</li>
        <li>Members benefit from useful content (weather, sports, course info)</li>
        <li>Revenue flows monthly with no effort from course staff</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We're expanding our golf network beyond ClubLink and looking for additional course partners across Canada — private clubs, resort courses, and premium public courses.</p>
      <a href="/golftv/clublinktv/" class="btn btn-primary">Learn more about ClubLinkTV</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="different-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What makes SDN different for golf courses</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Traditional golf course advertising usually means static sponsor boards in the parking lot or paper posters in the locker room. SDN is fundamentally different:</p>
      <div class="different-grid">
        <div class="different-card">
          <h3>Digital, not static</h3>
          <p>4K screens with dynamic, rotating content instead of faded sponsor boards</p>
        </div>
        <div class="different-card">
          <h3>National advertisers</h3>
          <p>Access to major brand budgets, not just local sign sales</p>
        </div>
        <div class="different-card">
          <h3>Zero cost</h3>
          <p>SDN pays for everything; your course pays nothing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="different-card">
          <h3>Zero effort</h3>
          <p>No selling, no installation logistics, no maintenance</p>
        </div>
        <div class="different-card">
          <h3>Useful content</h3>
          <p>Weather, scores, and course info that members actually want</p>
        </div>
        <div class="different-card">
          <h3>Revenue sharing</h3>
          <p>Guaranteed monthly payments</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Apply to add screens to your clubhouse</h2>
    <p>If your golf course is in a Canadian market with active membership or strong guest traffic, we'd like to discuss a partnership. Complete our application and we'll respond within two business days.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn-white">Apply now</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .intro-section p {
    color: var(--gray-600, #495057);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .why-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .why-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .why-card {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .why-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .why-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .install-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .install-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .install-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .install-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .install-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .install-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .install-note {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .content-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .content-section .section-intro {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .content-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .content-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .content-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  .content-note {
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .revenue-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .revenue-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .revenue-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .revenue-card {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .revenue-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .revenue-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .revenue-card ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }
  .revenue-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .factors-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .factors-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .factors-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .factor-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .factor-item strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .factor-item span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .clublink-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a472a 0%, #2d5a3f 100%);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .clublink-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .clublink-section > .container > p {
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .clublink-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .clublink-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }
  .clublink-list li::before {
    content: ">";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #8bc34a;
  }
  .clublink-section .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .different-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .different-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .different-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .different-card {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .different-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .different-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .revenue-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .factors-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
